{{zh-forms|[[朝]][[闻]][[道]]，[[夕]][[死]][[可]][[矣]]|[[朝聞道，夕死可矣]]}}
==Mandarin==
From: {{RQ:Confucius}}

===Proverb===
{{cmn-proverb|s|pin=zhāo wén dào, xì sĭ kĕ yĭ|pint=zhao1wen2dao4xi4si3ke3yi3|tra=朝聞道，夕死可矣|sim=朝闻道，夕死可矣|rs=月08}}
# If in the morning I were to gain knowledge of the correct path (in life), I would be able to die at sunset (without regrets).
